{{legend|#00e000;|[[Federazion|Stac federei]]}}]]N '''stat uniter''' ie n stat che vën guvernà coche na entità unica cun n guviern zentrel che à l'autorità. L guviern zentrel possa meter su o to demez dijivions aministratives y chëstes à mé la funzions che l guviern ti deleghea.<ref name="WorldAtlas">{{cite web |url=https://www.worldatlas.com/articles/what-is-a-unitary-state.html |title=What is a Unitary State? |website=WorldAtlas |date=August 2017 |access-date=2019-02-22}}</ref> 

N stat uniter ie desfrënt da na federazion, ënghe cunesciù coche stat federel. La majera pert di stac al mond (166 di 193 stac cumëmbri de la UNO) ie stac uniteres.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.un.org/en/sections/issues-depth/democracy/index.html |title=Democracy |date=2015-11-20 |website=www.un.org |access-date=2019-02-22 |archive-date=2021-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213090624/https://www.un.org/en/sections/issues-depth/democracy/index.html |url-status=dead }}</ref>


